	   <tr><td colspan=2>To the most honorable scribe and historian Naldiin Aredhel'istar:<br><br>I have consumed your works with both joy and trepidation.&nbsp;&nbsp;I would like you to clarify one item for me however, and that is regarding the statement saying that Sathir made a pact with Innoruuk.  Is this correct, or perhaps an overlooked error on your part?  The reason for the question is obvious, because the Iksar of today tend to follow the lord of Fear, not the lord of Hate.<br><br>Most humbly your student,<br>&nbsp;<br>Icewind Novastorm<br>Koada Dal Cleric of Tunare<br>&lt;&lt;Mith Marr&gt;&gt;</td></tr>
