	   <tr><td colspan=2>I've decided to use my journal as a place to gather information that most sites don't carry.<br><br>Interesting peice of game lore?&nbsp;&nbsp;Stories, etc?  site the source for it and post it.<br><br>Little known facts about a monster?  (no i don't care about VOx's breath weapon, but give me some Information on Mayong mistmoore while he was in game...and i will smile)<br><br>in-game books, tomes, scrolls that are readable (example, Book of Turmoil), tell me!  Give the name of the item, the content, and how it can be obtained.<br><br>And thats what the board is for.  In brief.  I'll be posting as well, on what i have.<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br>Naldiin Aredhel'istar<br>Magician, 52th Circle<br>&lt;Povar-Tarrew Artisiens&gt;<br>Xev Server</td></tr>
